ATL! We’re back from LA just in time for our favorite holiday! We’re taking the JUMPOFF energy back OUTSIDE for the Juneteenth Jumpoff!

Join us on Saturday, June 17th 4PM-10PM, as we we take over the Legendary Underground and transform it into a Jumpoff block party vibe! Enjoy 3 complimentary drinks valid til 6:30, Food Vendors, Dope DJs, and Good Energy! Soundtrack by @Abehyde + @Unruely_ + @genesisftl + @mrplay +@DJYungFro259! 

✨SPECIAL GUEST Performance by ATL’s own Young Dro !! 🎶 Don’t miss out on this one!!

🎟Limited Juneteenth Customer Appreciation tickets available now! GET YOUR TICKETS NOW!

For tickets and info, visit www.thejumpoffseries.com 

#TheJumpoffSeries #Juneteenth #ATL #Atlanta #DanceParty
